definition: to attain/to reach/to amount to/to communicate/eminent

sentences.english: The cases have been laboratory confirmed by the Institut Pasteur, Dakar.
sentences.chinese: 這些病例已得到達喀爾巴斯德研究所的實驗室確認。

sentences.english: Badiali says his goal is to capture 40 percent of the Dakar market.
sentences.chinese: 巴迪亞利表示，他的目標是控制40%的達喀爾市場。

sentences.english: Dakar is most affected, due to the unusually heavy rains.
sentences.chinese: 達喀爾由於異乎尋常的滂沱大雨受影響最嚴重。

sentences.english: How was your day?. My was little cold over here in Dakar Senegal.
sentences.chinese: 今天怎麼樣？。我是這裏有點冷在塞內加爾的達喀爾。

sentences.english: The case has been laboratory confirmed for Yellow fever by the Institut Pasteur, Dakar.
sentences.chinese: 達喀爾市巴斯德研究所實驗室確認了該起黃熱病病例。

sentences.english: Mine a little hot over here in Dakar Senegal.
sentences.chinese: 在達喀爾塞內加爾的這裏稍微熱地挖掘。

sentences.english: The proof is in the parking lot at the presidential palace in Dakar.
sentences.chinese: 相關證據就在達喀爾總統府的停車場裏。
